    "A tissue segmentation model was trained in similar fashion.",
    "Segmentations were downsampled with min pooling, to overestimate non-tissue regions at lower resolutions.",
    "Prior to alignment training and inference, the ssEM image stack is downsampled, masked, and normalized.",
    "First, the original images are downsampled through average pooling to produce a hierarchy of resolutions ranging up to 4096 nm.",
    "Next, discontinuous image defect masks and resin masks are produced by specialized convolutional networks."
